name: 8x10" Be Bold Print
description:
8x10" print of my original watercolor illustration. Sometimes you just need a reminder to be brave and live a life of adventure! Looks swell hanging next to my Be Brave print.

Printed with Epson inks on Canon high-resolution paper.

Please note: Final printed and mailed artwork will be signed and the watermark will be removed.
